{"tid":1442103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台山口音香港警察","createTime":"2019-08-10T22:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:06:10.000Z","uid":252834,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"df86175ec4275f6017da7e30e413a8fd23c66db4","tid":1442103,"uid":252834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:57:44.000Z","msg":"武警?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2195006407293226/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2195006407293226%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=22cfc663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2195006407293226/?sfnsn=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5953aca5a7fbd9bd9f01be30c265ccdce215b930","tid":1442103,"uid":23099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:59:12.000Z","msg":"黑社會 強姦犯 中共武裝份子"},{"pid":"1e07e77d56f6eab7b549b6ab232d976bad8dd8af","tid":1442103,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:59:57.000Z","msg":"文宣密密做 落場手足可唔可以都幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑狗屌老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca7e44ca96887918dfbfd45deb39dc8c850e99f6","tid":1442103,"uid":178368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:04:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"74dbe5693f085c785e12b0c858aa7832bf5012e6","tid":1442103,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"038e05f2b9254734e398986fc533ffb3e376e994","tid":1442103,"uid":24168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"應該去警察記者會問<br />\n<br />\n係唔係委任咗大陸人做特務警察<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/245/s41.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F245%2Fs41.html&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=8eac3caa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/245/s41.html</a><br />\n<br />\n第245章 《公安條例》 第40條 行政長官授權他人委任特務警察的權力<br />\n<br />\n行政長官可隨時藉命令授權警務處處長，以書面方式委任任何願意擔任特務警察的人為特務警察，任期由行政長官在該命令中指明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第245章 《公安條例》 第41條 特務警察的權力<br />\n<br />\n(1)獲委為特務警察的人，在以該身分行事時所具備的職責、權力、保障及豁免權，均與本條例或任何其他法律所委予或授予警務人員的職責、權力、保障及豁免權相同。<br />\n<br />\n(2)特務警察須遵從警務處處長向其作出的所有命令。<br />\n<br />\n(3)本條的規定並不使特務警察有權獲得任何薪酬、退休金或其他報酬。"},{"pid":"a130a0252b0448c191ad9c6ba94f784faac4ed0e","tid":1442103,"uid":258005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:26:18.000Z","msg":"無樣？<br />\n見過個鬼佬樣防暴係識講廣東話"},{"pid":"c0afa873df29e11bb28085d42eeecc8215d18cac","tid":1442103,"uid":194363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"似係識講廣東話個鬼佬"},{"pid":"d86bae5b66a0651aa814de73356a3bc083e731e1","tid":1442103,"uid":257811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"唔係台山口音"},{"pid":"afc352bee987abe6755dc515c4768e3a0f2ef148","tid":1442103,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6919a59a938e59361849ad2faa32496df4af8d42","tid":1442103,"uid":288742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"這篇文章已被刪除或無法載入。"},{"pid":"792b83570bf714c20b07c24de1900f357b0df6d3","tid":1442103,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:04:15.000Z","msg":"一定係 唔使懷疑"},{"pid":"e4c8923e5f58ae57060b21e72bca0b4ad593331c","tid":1442103,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:06:10.000Z","msg":"睇唔到"}]}